Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta halarci haikalin da ke rikice-rikice a shafin yanar gizo
Firayim Ministan Indiya Narendra Modi zai halarci bikin da ya dace a wata mai zuwa don haikalin Hindu a wani wurin da aka yi garkuwa da su a arewacin Indiya inda masallacin Hindu na karni na 16 ya rushe a shekarar 1992, bisa ga amincewar da ke kula da ginin haikalin.
An shirya bikin ne a ranar 5 ga watan Agusta, wanda ya shirya kwanan wata ya ce yana da goyon baya ga Hindu amma hakan kuma ya nuna shekara guda tun lokacin da Majalisar Indiya ta soke matsayi mai cin gashin kanta na jihar Musulmi kawai, Jammu da Kashmir.
Wannan alama ba zai yiwu a rasa magoya baya da masu adawa da Jam'iyyar Hindu ta Modi Bharatiya Janata ba, ko BJP, wanda bayaninsa ya yi shekaru da yawa ya hada da wa'adin da za a cire ikon sarrafa kansa na Kashmir da kuma gina haikali ga allahn Hindu Ram inda masallacin Mughal ya tashi, wani wuri a birnin Ayodhya a Uttar Pradesh.
Saboda coronavirus har yanzu yana ci gaba a duk faɗin Indiya, wanda ya ba da rahoton mafi girma a duniya, bikin za a watsa shirye-shiryen kai tsaye a talabijin na jihar kuma yawan mahalarta da masu kallo za a iyakance, a cewar Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko Hukumar Hindu ta Duniya, kungiyar Hindu ta kasa da ta haɗe da BJP.
Haikalin zai zama " cibiyar haskakawa na zamantakewa, haɗin kai da hadin gwiwa na kasa da farkawa da ji na Hindu," ko hanyar rayuwar Hindu, mai magana da yawun kungiyar Vinod Bansal, ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa a ranar Asabar.
An warware rikice-rikice na tsawon karni a kan shafin a shekarar da ta gabata bayan nasarar zaben BJP.
A watan Nuwamba, Kotun Koli ta yanke hukuncin amincewar haikalin, inda ta ce za a ba da aikace-aikacen Musulmai na akidar biyar a wani shafin madaidaiciya.
'Yan Hindu masu tsanani sun daɗe suna jayayya cewa masu mamaye Musulmi na Muhammadu sun gina masallaci a sama da wani haikali da ya kasance a tsohuwar birnin Ayodya.
Wani tashin hankali a watan Disamba 1992 bayan lalata masallacin ya haifar da tashin hankali na al'umma inda aka kashe kimanin mutane 2,000, galibi musulmi.
