OAKLAND, Ca. - Masu zanga-zangar a California sun kona kotu, sun lalata ofishin 'yan sanda da kuma harin jami'an tsaro bayan wani zanga-zangar zaman lafiya ya karu da yammacin ranar Asabar, in ji 'yan sanda na Oakland.
Masu nuna wa’azi sun karya tagogi, suna zanen zane-zane, sun harbe wasan wuta da kuma nuna lasers a jami’an, sashen Oakland ya ce a shafin Twitter.
Yawancin tweets sun kira zaman lafiya kuma sun bukaci masu shiryawa su "taimake mu samar da wuraren lafiya da wurare masu nunawa."
An fara zanga-zangar a ranar Asabar da yamma tare da kungiyoyi kamar "Wall of Moms," kama da rukunin da aka kafa a Portland, Oregon, yayin da masu zanga-zangar suka fuskanci jami'an Amurka da aka tura zuwa birnin don tsare kotun tarayya.
Shugaba Donald Trump ya aika da jami'an tarayya don dakatar da zanga-zangar da suka faru da dare tun bayan rasuwar George Floyd a Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu.
An fara zanga-zangar a Oakland cikin kwanciyar hankali, amma daga baya ya juya tashin hankali a cikin dare.
'Yan sanda sun sanar da "taron ba tare da izini ba" game da karfe 11:30 na yamma kuma jami'an sun nemi jama'a su warwatsa.
Wutar ta faru a Kotun Kotun Koli ta Alameda kuma an ɗauke shi a cikin ɗan gajeren lokaci bayan haka, in ji labarai.
'Yan sanda sun ce masu zanga-zangar a wani lokaci suna "fashe windows da kuma waƙoƙin launin fata a mazauna."
