Tsaro mai tsaro a waje da majalisar dokokin Amurka a Chengdu, kasar Sin
Akwai matsayi mai tsaro a waje da kwamitin Amurka a birnin Chengdu, China ranar Lahadi, yayin da ma'aikatan Amurka ke shirye su bar dakin.
An ga motoci uku masu motsawa suna shiga cikin ɗakin ginin, yayin da 'yan sanda masu tsalle-tsalle da' yan sanda suka yi layi biyu na titi, waɗanda aka yi layi da shinge na karfe.
Editan jaridar Global Times ta kasar Sin ya rubuta cewa an ba da kwamitin hukumar Amurka a Chengdu na sa'o'i 72 don rufewa, ko har zuwa 10 na safe (0200 GMT) Litinin, Yuli 27.
Kasar Sin ta ce wasu ma'aikata a Kwankwaso na Chengdu sun "yi aiki ba tare da la'akari da halayensu ba."
Ba tare da ba da cikakken bayani ba, mai magana da yawun ma'aikatar harkokin waje ta kasar Sin, Wang Wenbin ya ce irin wannan aiki ya shiga harkokin kasar Sin kuma ya cutar da bukatun tsaro.
An bayar da umarnin da kasar Sin ta rufe takunkumi a Chengdu a ranar Juma'a don mayar da martani ga umarnin Amurka don rufe takunkumi na kasar Sin a Houston, Texas.
Washington ta umarci China ta rufe ofishin Houston "don kare dukiyar ilimin Amurka da bayanan sirri na Amurka."
Yayin da rufe hukumar kwamitin kasar Sin a Houston ta fara aiki a ranar Juma'a, an ga wani rukuni na maza da suka bayyana jami'an Amurka sun shiga ɗakin ta hanyar ƙofar baya.
Wang ya bayyana a ranar Asabar cewa ta keta yarjejeniyar kasa da kasa da na biyu, kuma China za ta amsa, ba tare da bayyana yadda.
