Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ce dubban 'yan adawa da Pakistan a Afghanistan
Rahotanni na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sun ce sama da 'yan tawayen Pakistan 6,000 ne ke boyewa a Afghanistan, mafi yawansu na kungiyar Taliban da ke da alhakin kai hare-haren sojojin Pakistan da farar hula.
Rahoton da aka fitar a wannan makon ya ce kungiyar, wanda aka fi sani da Tehreek-e-Taliban (TTP), ta danganta da dangantaka da kungiyar da ke Afghanistan.
Wasu daga cikin mambobin TTP har ma sun shiga dangin IS, wanda ke da hedkwatarsa a gabashin Afghanistan.
Gwamnatin Afghanistan ba ta amsa tambayoyin da Associated Press ya yi ba a ranar Lahadi.
Rahoton ya ce IS a Afghanistan, wanda aka fi sani da IS a lardin Khorasan, sojojin tsaro na Afghanistan da sojojin Amurka da NATO, har ma a wani lokaci Taliban na Afghanistan.
Hukumar kula da takunkumi ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta shirya rahoton, wanda ke bin kungiyoyin ta'addanci a fadin duniya.
Rahoton ya kiyasta cewa membobin IS a Afghanistan sun kai 2,200, kuma yayin da aka gaji shugabancinta, IS har yanzu yana daga cikin shugabanninta na kasar Siriya Abu Said Mohammad al-Khorasani.
Rahoton ya kuma ce kungiyar sa ido ta samu bayanai cewa manyan kwamandan gwamnatin Musulunci guda biyu, Abu Qutaibah da Abu Hajar al-Iraqi, kwanan nan sun isa Afghanistan daga Gabas ta Tsakiya.
"Kodayake a yankunan da suka dace, (Shaharar Musulunci) har yanzu yana iya gudanar da hare-haren da aka yi a sassa daban-daban na kasar, ciki har da Kabul.
Har ila yau, yana nufin jawo hankalin mayakan Taliban da ke adawa da yarjejeniyar da Amurka," in ji rahoton, yana nufin yarjejeniyar zaman lafiya ta Amurka da aka sanya hannu kan Taliban a watan Fabrairu.
An kafa wannan yarjejeniyar don ba da damar Amurka ta kawo karshen shigarta na shekaru 19 a Afghanistan, kuma ta yi kira ga Taliban da ta tabbatar da cewa ba za a yi amfani da yankinta ba.
Hakanan ana sa ran yarjejeniyar ta tabbatar da kasancewar Taliban a cikin yaki da IS.
Sashe na biyu kuma watakila mafi mahimmancin yarjejeniyar yana buƙatar tattaunawa tsakanin Taliban da shugabancin siyasa na Kabul.
A baya Asabar, Ma'aikatar Harkokin Waje ta Amurka ta bayar da sanarwar cewa manzonta Zalmay Khalilzad ya sake kaiwa yankin da ke neman tsalle-tsalle don fara waɗannan tattaunawa, waɗanda aka dawo da su sau da yawa yayin da bangarorin biyu ke tattaunawa kan shirin sakin fursuna.
Yarjejeniyar da Amurka ta tallafawa gwamnatin Afghanistan ta saki fursunonin Taliban 5,000 da Taliban su saki ma'aikatan gwamnati da sojoji 1,000 a matsayin abin da ake kira kyakkyawan zaɓe kafin tattaunawa.
Ya zuwa yanzu gwamnatin ta ƙi saki kusan fursunonin Taliban 600 da ta kira manyan masu aikata laifuka kuma ta ba da kyautar zaɓi.
Taliban ta ƙi.
"Masu zanga-zangar sun fi kusa da fara tattaunawa tsakanin Afghanistan, babban mataki na gaba don kawo karshen yakin Afghanistan na tsawon shekaru 40," in ji jawabin Ma'aikatar Harkokin Waje ta Amurka.
"Kodayake an samu ci gaba mai muhimmanci a kan musayar fursunoni, batun yana buƙatar ƙarin kokarin warwarewa gaba ɗaya."
Mai magana da yawun siyasa na Taliban a farkon wannan makon ya ce yana shirye ya gudanar da tattaunawa da shugabannin siyasa na Kabul bayan hutun Musulunci na Eid al-Adha a karshen watan, inda ya samar da sakin fursunoni.
Babban damuwa ga Pakistan shine kasancewar 'yan bindiga a Afghanistan, musamman dangane da TTP ko Jamat-ul-Ahrar ko Lashkar-e-Islam, da kuma wadanda ke da rundunar 'yantar da Baluchistan, wanda ya dauki alhakin hare-haren a wannan watan a lardin Sindh da kuma lardin Baluchistan ta kudu.
An kashe sojojin Pakistan da dama a wannan watan a lardin kudu maso yammacin Baluchistan a yaki da 'yan tawaye.
TTP ya dauki alhakin daya daga cikin hare-haren da suka fi muni a Pakistan a shekarar 2014, lokacin da aka kai hari a makarantar sojojin Pakistan kuma an kashe 140.
Yawancin ɗalibai ne, kuma wasu sun kasance matasa 5.
"Tsarin adadin 'yan ta'addan kasashen waje na Pakistan a Afghanistan, wanda ke fuskantar barazana ga kasashe biyu, an kiyasta tsakanin 6,000 zuwa 6,500, mafi yawansu tare da TTP," in ji rahoton.
