Babban bankin HSBC da ke birnin London ya kai ga kafofin watsa labarun ya ce ba shine, kamar yadda kafofin watsa labarai na kasar Sin suka yi ikirarin, "mai shaida" a kan Huawei, wanda ya haifar da kama babban jami'in kudi na kamfanin a Kanada.
A cikin wani sakon da ba a samuwa a yanzu ba a kan WeChat, mai ba da bashi ya ce ayyukansa ba ya haifar da bincike na Amurka a kan mafi girman mai ba da kayan aikin sadarwa na sadarwa a duniya, yayin da binciken Huawei na zargin keta takunkumin Amurka a kan Iran ya fara sosai kafin shiga bankin a ƙarshen 2016.
"HSBC ba shi da wani adawa da Huawei kuma ba shi da "frame" Huawei," in ji bankin a ranar Asabar, wanda ya kara da cewa ba zai taɓa rushe duk wani gaskiya game da abokan cinikinsa ba.
"A mayar da martani ga buƙatun [Ma'aikatar Shari'a ta Amurka] na DOJ don bayanai, HSBC Group kawai ya gabatar da gaskiyar manufar.
