An toshe shafin akan dandamali tare da rubutu cewa yana "ta ƙetare dokoki" kuma ba a samuwa a yanzu ba.
Sanarwar ta zo ba da daɗewa ba bayan kafofin watsa labarun kasar Sin da yawa, ciki har da jaridu da ke da alaka da jihar, sun zargi HSBC da "tattaunawa" da Washington don kafa tarko ga Huawei.
Kamfanin ya kasance a cikin cibiyar tashin hankali na diflomasiyya fiye da shekara guda da rabi tun lokacin da aka kama Huawei CFO Meng Wanzhou a watan Disamba 2018 a Kanada bisa umarni daga Amurka.
Meng yana fuskantar zargin zamba da zargin yin amfani da kamfanin shell don karyata takunkumin kan Iran da kuma zargin ƙarya ga bankuna game da dangantaka tsakanin Huawei da kamfanin Skycom na Iran.
A cewar sabon shaida da aka ambata ta Global Times, HSBC ya san dangantakar kamfanin China da Skycom.
An ruwaito cewa bankin ya zaɓi "tattaunawa" tare da gwamnatin Amurka don tserewa daga tsananin hukunci a shekarar 2012, lokacin da bankin ya yarda da lalata kuɗi da takunkumi, ciki har da takunkumi kan Iran.
An umarce shi a lokacin da ya biya kusan dala biliyan 1.9 a cikin hukunci da kuma hana kowane irin wannan mummunan aiki.
"Takaddun shaida sun nuna cewa HSBC ta fahimci wannan dangantaka amma ta da niyyar sayar da takardun kasuwancin abokin ciniki na Amurka ga gefen Amurka don gwamnatin Amurka za ta iya manta da mummunan ayyukan bankin Burtaniya kuma ba za ta azabtar da shi ba a ƙarƙashin yarjejeniyar shari'a ta 2012," in ji jaridar.
A cikin gargadi mai zurfi, jaridar da ke kula da Beijing ta kara da cewa, idan mai ba da bashi ya tabbatar da laifin wannan "tattaunawa," zai iya fuskantar "azaba mai tsanani" a kasar Sin, daya daga cikin manyan kasuwanni na HSBC.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da bankin da aka fi sani da shi ba a cikin makonni da suka gabata.
A watan da ya gabata, an yi wa HSBC tallafawa sabuwar dokar tsaro ta kasar Hong Kong, birnin da kasuwancinta ya fara kuma wanda ya bayar da fiye da rabin riba.
Bankin ya fuskanci zargi daga bangarorin biyu - daga Yammacin Amurka, tare da sakataren harkokin wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya kira amincewar "kamfanin kowtow," da kuma Gabas, tare da bangaren kasar Sin da aka ruwaito cewa goyon baya "yana goyon baya."
