"Duk wadannan halaye da darajar sun sami marigayi Mahmoud Guemama girmamawa da amincewa da mutanen Tamanrasset wanda ya zabi shi don wakiltar su a Majalisar Kasa ta Jama'a (APN) na wasu lokuta, inda ya kasance jakadan da ke kare damuwa na yankin da kuma burin mutanensa, har ma da wakilin da mai magana da yawun Aljeniya," in ji shugaban kasar Jamhu.
"Duk maganganun ta'aziyya ba za su isa su ba da godiya ga Mujahed Mahmoud Guemama ba, salama a gare shi.
Yau yana barinmu a lokacin da Aljeriya ke buƙatar shi," in ji shugaban.
"Ina rokon Allah Madaukakin Sarki ya kewaye mutumin da ya mutu da rahamarSa Mai Tsarki, ya maraba da shi a cikin Aljanna mai girma tare da shuhadaa da mai kyau."
Na kuma yi addu'a ga Allah ya ba da iyalinsa da ƙaunatattunsa haƙuri da ta'aziyya ... babu karfi ko iko sai dai a wurin Allah," in ji Shugaban Jamhuriyar.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta yi zanga-zanga: Wuta da Pepper Spray kamar yadda Dubban Dubun Maris ta Birnin
Bayan makonni na rikice-rikice tsakanin masu zanga-zangar da hukumomin tarayya a Portland, Ore, taron mutane kusan 2,000 sun taru a Seattle a ranar Asabar, suna tafiya a kan tituna da rikice-rikice tare da 'yan sanda.
An ji rauni jami'an 'yan sanda uku, ciki har da wanda aka kwashe asibiti tare da rauni na kafafu, kuma an kama masu zanga-zangar 16 tun da dare, in ji 'yan sanda.
Dauke da alamomi kamar "Feds Go Home" da kuma kiran "Babu adalci, babu zaman lafiya," masu zanga-zangar sun tsaya a wurin cibiyar tsare matasa na gaba kuma sun ƙone gine-gine a can.
Wasu kamfanonin da ke kusa da taga sun rushe.
'Yan sanda sun fuskanci jama'a a cikin unguwannin Capitol Hill, suna aiwatar da rumbun wuta da tufafi na tufafi kafin su fara kama mutane a kurkuku.
Bipasha Mukherjee, mai shekaru 52, mai suna Kirkland, Wash, ta ce tana zanga-zangar kan tituna tun daga watan Mayu kuma ta ce tana damuwar ganin irin wannan dabarun da 'yan sanda ke yi.
"Wannan ba ƙasar da na yi hijira ba ce," in ji Mrs Mukherjee, wanda ya isa daga Indiya fiye da shekaru 30 da suka gabata.
"Muna jin kamar mun zama jihar fashist da kuma jihar 'yan sanda."
Michaud Savage na Seattle ya ce zanga-zangar ana nufin hukumomin gida biyu da kuma tura jami'an tarayya wadanda suka yi rikici kan zanga-zangar da suka yi na dogon lokaci a Portland.
Mista Savage ya ce dabarun aiwatar da doka a Portland, wanda ya haɗa da amfani da iskar gas da bindigogi masu iko, suna da haɗari kuma ba su dace ba.
"Shi ne mai wuya a cikin jagora mai tsanani," Mr. Savage ya ce yayin da yake wanke idanunsa na spray na pepper kuma ya kula da raunuka a hannunsa daga dutse mai haske.
Mutuwar George Floyd a tsare da 'yan sanda a Minneapolis a watan Mayun ya ƙone zanga-zangar jama'a da suka jawo miliyoyin zuwa tituna a garuruwa da dama, amma waɗannan zanga-zangar sun ragu a yawancin birane.
Koyaya, Seattle da Portland sun ga zanga-zangar da yawa.
'Yan zanga-zangar Seattle a wani lokaci sun yi ikirarin da aka yi wa 'yan sanda da dama na unguwannin Capitol Hill kuma sun bayyana yankin mai cin gashin kanta.
Bayan wani jerin hare-haren a can ya jagoranci 'yan sanda su tsare yankin, zanga-zangar sun ragu.
Har ila yau, Portland ta ci gaba da zanga-zangar, tare da wasu daga cikin manyan zanga-zangar da ke kusa da gine-ginen tarayya a birnin.
Bayan Shugaba Trump ya ba da umarnin zartarwa don kare asusu da dukiyar tarayya, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta gida ta tura kungiyoyin dabarun zuwa ga birnin, inda suka fara jerin rikice-rikice da suka haifar da rauni ga masu zanga-zangar, binciken mai bincike da kuma kira daga shugabannin gida don jami'an tarayya su bar.
Mutanen da ke cikin wannan birnin sun yi zanga-zanga har zuwa dubban dubban, kuma zanga-zangar sun ci gaba.
A wannan makon, jami'an tarayya sun tura tawagar dabarun zuwa Seattle, kuma masu zanga-zangar sun ambaci wannan ci gaba a matsayin dalilin gudanar da zanga-zangar ranar Asabar.
Yayin da zanga-zangar Portland ke tsakiya a tsakiyar birnin, zanga-zangar a ranar Asabar ta yi yankuna gabas da tsakiyar birnin, inda kotun tarayya ta birnin ke.
