'Yan bindiga' sun dakatar da binciken kwayoyin cutar coronavirus
Amurka ta yi kokarin samar da magungunan magani masu amfani saboda masu bincike suna gwada magungunan a cikin "hanyar da ba ta dace ba," in ji gwani wanda ke jagorantar shirin Birtaniya.
Shirin Bincike na Birtaniya, wanda ya haɗa da marasa lafiya 12,000 a asibitoci da yawa na Birtaniya, ya riga ya nuna sabon miyagun ƙwayoyi don magance cutar kuma ya nuna wasu biyu - wanda a baya ake tsammani zai iya ceto rayuwa - kamar yadda ba su da amfani.
Amma gazawar tsarin likita na Amurka don daidaita wannan samfurin yana nufin cewa wasu magani masu alkawari da za a iya share don amfani dashi har yanzu ba a kimanta su ba.
Musamman, plasma mai laushi ( jini plasma da aka dauka daga marasa lafiya na Covid-19 kuma wanda ke dauke da kwayoyin cuta waɗanda zasu iya kare wasu daga cutar) har yanzu ya kamata a gwada su yadda ya kamata a kan babban gwajin da aka yi.
"An riga an ba dubban dubban mutane plasma mai warkewa a Amurka amma waɗannan magani ba a ba da shawara ba," in ji Farfesa Martin Landray, ɗaya daga cikin wadanda suka kafa shirin dawowa.
"Sun kawai ba mutane kwance plasma a cikin begen cewa zai yi aiki. An ba da yawa kuma har yanzu ba su san ko yana taimakawa ko lalacewa ko ba shi da tasiri," in ji Landray, gwani a kan kafa manyan gwaje-gwaje na miyagun ƙwayoyi.
Amurka ta kasa yin manyan gwaje-gwaje, kuma wannan ya ƙare yana ba da magani mara kyau.
Gwajin miyagun ƙwayoyi na asali shine misali na zinariya don nuna magunguna masu amfani.
Suna cire abubuwan da ba a sani ba waɗanda za su iya yanke hukuncin likitoci na girgije.
Dubban mutane suna ba da miyagun ƙwayoyi kuma dubban mutane suna ba da placebo.
Ya san ba wani gwajin da aka yi kwanan nan.
Sa'an nan kuma ana kwatanta sakamakon kuma tasirin magani ya bayyana.
Ta wannan hanyar, Recovery ya iya nuna cewa steroid dexamethasone ya rage mutuwar mutum na uku a cikin marasa lafiya na Covid-19 akan ventilators.
Har ila yau, ya nuna cewa maganin hydroxychloroquine - kazalika da hadewar maganin lopinavir da ritonavir - ba su da tasiri wajen ceton rayukan marasa lafiya.
Wadannan gwaje-gwaje suna buƙatar yawancin marasa lafiya kuma babu wani asibiti guda da ke da isasshen irin wannan bincike.
Birtaniya tana da fa'idodi guda ɗaya - ma'aikatar kiwon lafiya ta ƙasa.
Sabanin haka, sabis ɗin kiwon lafiyar Amurka ya ragu kuma kawai nasararta a nuna wata magani mai yiwuwa an nuna amfani da miyagun ƙwayoyi masu tsada na remdesivir don sauri dawo da wasu marasa lafiya na Covid-19.
"Akwai da yawa kananan gwaje-gwaje na kwayoyi da suka shafi 'yan goma ko' yan daruruwan marasa lafiya da ke faruwa a Amurka amma babu wani abu," in ji Landray.
"Sun kasa yin manyan gwaje-gwaje, kuma wannan ya ƙare samar da mummunan magani. Yana sa aikin magani ya fi talauci da sakamakon marasa lafiya ya fi talauci."
Landray ya ce wannan gazawar tana da matukar damuwa musamman lokacin da ya zo ga amfani da plasma mai warkewa, wanda likitoci da yawa sun yi imanin cewa za su iya taka muhimmiyar rawa wajen magance marasa lafiya na COVID-19.
"Idan ka dubi Amurka, yawancin wannan magani an yi amfani da su a kan wani m willy-nilly tushen. Birtaniya ta fi girma fiye da ma'auni idan aka kwatanta da abin da ke faruwa a can," in ji shi.
Farfesa Peter Horby, gwani a kan cututtuka masu kamuwa da cututtuka da kuma sauran wanda ya kafa shirin Recovery, ya ce: "Akwai rahotanni game da marasa lafiya 20,000 da ke samun plasma mai warkewa a cikin wani rukuni amma babu ɗaya daga cikin waɗannan marasa lafiya da aka yi.
Idan sun sanya wadannan marasa lafiya a cikin gwaji na musamman, yanzu muna da amsar bayyananne game da tasiri na plasma mai laushi. "
Horby ya kara da cewa UK Recovery yanzu ya kaddamar da gwaji na plasma mai laushi amma ba ya tsammanin sakamakon zai kasance a shirye har zuwa ƙarshen wannan shekara.
Masar ta fara rajista bayanan masu jefa kuri'a a waje don zaben majalisar dattawa
