Batun da ya fi dacewa ga masu shari'a - da kuma batun jayayya tsakanin 'yan Republican da Democrats - shine ƙarewar fa'idodin rashin aikin yi, wanda ya fara tafi a karshen mako.
Duk da yake 'yan Democrat suna son kunshin coronavirus na "zagaye hudu" don ci gaba da bunkasa dala 600 zuwa fa'idodin, 'yan Republican suna kiran a dawo da shi kuma suna jayayya da wasu Amurkawa suna yin fiye da rashin aikin yi fiye da yadda suka yi a albashi.
Cruz ya ce fiye da rabi na Amurkawa da ke karɓar fa'idodin rashin aikin yi ana biya su yanzu fiye da lokacin da suke aiki kuma ya ce yana magana da kananan masu kasuwanci a Texas waɗanda ke da matsaloli na sake yin ma'aikata.
