AURORA, Colo. (AP) - Mota ta shiga taron jama'a kuma an harbe mai zanga-zangar a gundumar Denver na Aurora a lokacin zanga-zangar kan rashin adalci na launin fata.
Sashen 'yan sanda na Aurora ya bayyana a shafin Twitter cewa masu zanga-zangar suna tafiya a kan Interstate 225 a ranar Asabar lokacin da wata mota ta shiga.
'Yan sanda sun ce wani mai zanga-zangar ya harbe makami, inda akalla mutum daya da aka kai shi asibiti a cikin yanayi na kwanciyar hankali.
Hukumomin sun ce an kama motar kuma suna bincike.
Har ila yau, masu zanga-zangar sun karya taga zuwa gidan kotu kuma an fara wuta a ofishin, in ji 'yan sanda.
An sanar da taron ba bisa doka ba kuma 'yan sanda sun umurci masu zanga-zangar su bar yankin, hukumomi suka ce.
An kara tsananta tashin hankali a kan zanga-zangar da ake yi wa zalunci a baya-bayan nan tun lokacin da aka aika da jami'an tarayya don kawar da zanga-zangar a Portland, Oregon.
'Yan sanda sun sanar da wani tashin hankali a Seattle ranar Asabar.
An yi zanga-zanga da mutuwar George Floyd a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu, wani baƙar fata a Minnesota wanda ya mutu bayan wani jami'in fari ya kama shi ƙasa tare da gwiwa a wuyansa, ya kuma nuna wasu lokuta na tashin hankalin 'yan sanda.
A Colorado, masu zanga-zangar suna jawo hankalin mutuwar Elias McClain, wanda 'yan sanda suka dakatar da shi yayin da suke tafiya a titin Aurora a watan Agusta 2019 bayan wani mai kira 911 ya ba shi rahoto a matsayin mai shakka.
'Yan sanda sun sanya shi a cikin chokehold, kuma likitoci sun gudanar da miliyan 500 na ketamin, magani, don ya kwashe shi.
