Duk da haka wannan gidan wasan kwaikwayo na Girka ya samar da sauti mai ƙarfi da fushi.
A matakinsa, wasan kwaikwayo ya buga kamar bugun hasken rana, daukar numfashinka - tasiri yana da ɗan gajeren lokaci ta kallon yanar gizo.
Na farko da aka samar a cikin 472 BC, ana ɗaukar "The Persians" a matsayin tsohuwar wasan Girka da ya tsira.
An watsa wannan wasan kwaikwayo na Dimitris Lignadis a ranar Asabar daga tsohuwar amphitheater na Epidaurus; a cikin ruhun gidan wasan kwaikwayo, babu rikodi akan layi.
An fara ɗaukar wurin a matsayin wani ɓangare na asclepeion na birnin (cibiyar warkarwa) saboda Helenawa suna la'akari da daidaituwa tsakanin jiki da rai da ke da muhimmanci ga lafiya.
Bari mu yi la'akari da wannan falsafar.
Wasan kwaikwayo yayi magana da bayan Salamis, yakin teku wanda Helenawa da suka fi yawa suka jagoranci sojojin Farisa shekaru 2,500 da suka gabata.
A lokacin da sararin samaniya ke rufewa, yana da matukar haifar da kusan shiga masu sauraro masu zaman kansu a kallon wasan kwaikwayo na rayuwa (tambaya) yayin da suke yin wasan kwaikwayo na dubban shekaru.
Aeschylus kansa ya yi yaƙi a Salamis, amma wasansa yana da juyawa: Wannan tsohuwar tsohuwar ɓangaren nasara ya kafa labarinsa daga cikin wadanda aka ci nasara, yana sanya ido mai tausayi a kan abokan gābansa na kwanan nan.
Wani waƙoƙi na maza na Farisa, suna sa tufafi masu tsawo, masu launi da fararen riguna, yana buɗe ayyukan.
Suna cikin babban birninsu suna jiran labari daga Sarkinsu, Xerxes, wanda ke waje da shi tare da Athens.
Shiga mahaifiyar Xerxes, Sarauniya Atossa (Lydia Koniordou), a cikin tufafin baƙar fata mai girma wanda ya nuna ta, maimakon baya; ita mutum ce a cikin wani exoskeleton na masana'anta, duka biyu masu rauni da ban mamaki.
Koniordou, wanda ke cikin manyan 'yan wasan kwaikwayo na Girka, ya san rawar da ke cikin waje - ta jagoranci kuma ta fito a cikin wani wasan kwaikwayo na ƙasa na Girka na "The Persians" wanda ya buga New York City Center a 2006 - kuma ta ba da tabbacin halayen ba tare da yin alama ba.
Yawancin lokaci, ta tsaya a tsakiyar mataki na zagaye, tana nuna fushi mai zurfi da baƙin ciki kamar yadda aka bayyana bala'in da ya faru da sojojin gida.
An tabbatar da damuwa ga kowa da kowa, a cikin cikakken bayani, ta hanyar wani manzo (Argyris Pandazaras) ya dawo daga gaban.
A cikin wani wuri mai ban sha'awa, ya ba da labari game da yaƙin, ya yi wa kansa cikin frenzy yayin da 'yan wasan kwaikwayo kewaye da shi kuma Giorgos Poulios's drone-like score ya tashi zuwa abin da dole ne ya kasance matakin deafening.
Daga baya mijin Atossa (Nikos Karathanos), wanda aka kira daga duniyar duniya, da Xerxes (Argyris Xafis), wanda ya tsere da rai daga fashewar.
Sassa na layi a kan jininsa na alama mai launin tonic (wasu kayan ado na Eva Nathena koyaushe suna ba da gudummawa ga labarun labari).
Mutane suna baƙin ciki da rasa rayuka da lalacewa tare, a cikin ayyuka na makoki na al'umma.
Kadan daga cikin gidan wasan kwaikwayo na gargajiya da muke gani a Amurka yana ƙoƙarin sa shi ya fi sauƙi a hanya ɗaya ko wani.
Sau da yawa ana yin wannan tare da karatun layi na halitta, don ƙoƙarin sanya rubutun ƙasashen waje, sauki a zubar da ciki.
Amma Lignadis da ƙungiyarsa sun karɓi rawar da ke da kyau, wanda zai iya zama ɗan tilastawa ga kunnuwan zamani amma yana nuna ikon rubutun.
Duk da yake fasaha ba su raira waƙa ba, alal misali, manyan 'yan wasan hudu sun ba da arias, suna samun iko mai ban sha'awa wanda ke jin sauran duniya.
Duk da haka, ba mu taɓa mantawa da cewa wasan kwaikwayo yana da mahimmanci a cikin motsin zuciyar mutum.
